para_trans: Transfer / posting to the cadre of Secretary and Secretary equivalent (Technical).
GOVERNMENT ORDER NUMBER: TRANSFER-4425 / P.No.132 / SERVICE-1
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Regulation of transfers and discharge of government duties of Maharashtra Government employees.
Pursuant to the provisions of sections 4 (4) and 4 (5) of the Prevention of Delay Act, 2005 and
With the approval of the Authority, the Secretary and Secretary (Technical) in the Public Works Department shall be
Substitution of the officer mentioned in the following table in the cadre in the interest of public service and
For administrative reasons, his name appears in front of Column No. The position shown in 4 is being done.
This Government Order is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
table_trans: Secretary (Construction), Public Works Department, Mantralaya, Mumbai.
Secretary (Roads), Public Works Department, Mantralaya, Mumbai. (Vacancies)
